er.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403121913\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.093 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.321 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1130/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10798/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 10498/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1108/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 13/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 3806/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.200/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.45 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  306.067      1 -total\n 95.11%  291.109      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 94.43%  289.008      1 Template:Infobox\n 13.08%   40.021     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  5.82%   17.803     10 Template:Ref\n  5.18%   15.863      4 Template:Infobox_label\n  3.35%   10.242     10 Template:Ref/core\n  1.25%    3.832      1 Template:References\n  0.31%    0.958      1 Template:Main_other\n  0.22%    0.685      2 Template:Nowrap\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:4717-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403121913 and revision id 297927\n -->\n",
